description:
IT'S RHONY PREMIERE WEEK AND THE ONE AND ONLY COUNTESS LUANN IS ON EVERYTHING ICONIC! Danny talks to Lu about the upcoming season, her relationship with Bethenny, what happened with Chicago, her thoughts on the Suez Canal, and SO much more! After Lu, Danny sits down with the hosts of MTV's Catfish, Nev and Kamie, to talk about celebrity catfishing, the upcoming season, and more!


Countess Luann: 6:40ish

Nev & Kamie from Catfish: 31:20ish
